  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air, then boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat, then once hot, add your <strong>coriander seeds</strong> and<strong> fennel seeds</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant and toasted, then transfer to a <strong>food processor</strong> and reserve the pan for later</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2415Step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
