          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped shallot</strong>, <strong>tomato</strong>, <strong>ginger</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong> to the<strong> food processor</strong> with the <strong>toasted spices</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> and blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>spice paste</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly<strong> </strong>(if required!)</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>creamed coconut</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2415Step-4-x200.jpg",
