            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Keralan-style chicken curry</strong> over the <strong>lime & chilli rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
